" +++++++++++++++++++++++++ Vim Config Statements +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
"
" Make Sure that Vim returns to the same line when we reopen a file
augroup line_return
  au!
  au BufReadPost *
  \ if line("'\"") > 0 && line("'\"") <= line("$") |
    \ execute 'normal! g`"zvzz' |
  \ endif
augroup END
"
" From vim-sensible Prob dont need or at lest dont need them to be if else
